All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Album
Album is a class that is used for making an Album-object, and is defined as an entity, so that objects of this class can be mapped to a relation database-table
AlbumDAO
AlbumDAO is a class which is used as a connection between the Album class and the database.
AlbumItem
AlbumItem is a class which extends Button to apply a button's traits.
DatabaseConnection
DatabaseConnection is a class which makes a database connection to all classes using the DatabaseConnection class Used to obtain an EntityManagerFactory in Java SE environments (EntityManagerFactory only exists to support instantiation of an EntityManager) EntityManager is used to represent a connection to a database
GeoConverter
GeoConverter is a class which converts latitude and longitude to a real address
ImageItem
ImageItem is a class which extends Button to apply a button's traits.
ImageMetaData
ImageMetaData is a class which is used to collect all metadata from a image, using the Metadata-extractor API
ImageV2
ImageV2 is a class that is used for making an ImageV2-object, and is defined as an entity, so that objects of this class can be mapped to a relation database-table
ImageV2DAO
ImageV2DAO is a class which connects ImageV2 (and Album) class to a database.
ImageV2Tests
ImageV2Tests is a test-class that uses JUnit-tests for some of the methods in our application
InformationDialog
InformationDialog is a class which makes a dialog window.
Main
The Main class has the task of launching the whole application.
MainMenuSceneController
MainMenuSceneController controls the MainMenuScene.
MapSceneController
MapSceneController controls the mapScene.
SearchAlbumController
SearchAlbumController covers all methods which are needed to run AlbumScene properly.
SearchImageSceneController
SearchImageSceneController controls the SearchImageScene.
SearchListItem  
UploadSceneController
UploadSceneController controls the UploadScene.
WindowMenuButtonsController
WindowsMenyButtonsController controls the window-menu-buttons
